Kh","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":13297,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/03\/faith-allah-make-use-wicked-man\/","url_meta":{"origin":2869,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Allah may bring good through a wicked man","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 3, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, no one will enter Paradise but a soul submissive to Allah, yet Allah may support this religion by the hands of a wicked man.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3062, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 111 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10810,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/28\/jihad-protect-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":2869,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: The Prophet fights to protect Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have been commanded to fight the people until they say there is no God but Allah. If they say there is no God but Allah, then they will be granted protection from me for their lives\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":457,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/27\/essentials-pillars-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":2869,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Essentials of salvation are pillars of Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A bedouin\u00a0came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, show me a deed by which I may enter Paradise.\u201d The Prophet said,\u00a0\u201cWorship Allah and never associate anything with Him, establish the prescribed prayers, give the obligatory\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2084,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/17\/five-pillars-of-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":2869,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Religion of Islam is built on five pillars","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIslam is built upon five: to worship Allah and to disbelieve in what is worshiped besides Him, to establish prayer, to give charity, to perform the Hajj pilgrimage to the house, and to fast the month\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Featured&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Featured","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/featured\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7625,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/dawah-hidayah-islam-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":2869,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Da&#8217;wah: Guiding a person to Islam better than all wealth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sahl ibn Sa\u2019d reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBy Allah, that Allah guides a man through you is better for you than a herd of expensive red camels.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3009, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2406 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2158,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/22\/helping-poor-jihad-fi-sabil-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":2869,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: Helping the poor is jihad in the way of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"One who lends effort to the widows and the poor is like one waging jihad in the way of Allah, or one who regularly prays at night and fasts during the day.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5353,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2869","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"a